<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
   <div class="container1">
    <div class="header">
      <h1> Sushirama</h1>
    </div> 
    <div class="menu">
      <h3>General Sushi</h3>
      <div class="menu-item">
      <p> Sashimi $5.99 Each</p>
      <button id="addsashimi" onclick="addsashimi()">Add Item</button>
      <button id="removesashimi" onclick="removesashimi()">Remove Item</button>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-item">
      <p> Nigiri $3.99 Each</p>
      <button id="addnigiri" onclick="addnigiri()">Add Item</button>
      <button id="removenigiri" onclick="removenigiri()">Remove Item</button>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-item">
      <p> Sushi Roll $4.99 Each</p>
      <button id="addsroll" onclick="addsroll()">Add Item</button>
      <button id="removesroll" onclick="removesroll()">Remove Item"</button>
      </div>
      <div class="menu-item">
      <p> Oysters $1.99 Each</p>
      <button id="addoyster" onclick="addo()">Add Item</button>
      <button id="removeoyster" onclick="removeo()">Remove Item</button>
      </div>
    </div> 
    <div class="ramen">
      <h3>General Ramen</h3>
      <p> Chicken Ramen $5.99</p>
      <p> Seafood Ramen $7.99</p>
      <p> Beef Ramen $8.99</p>
      <p> Veg Ramen $4.99</p>
    </div> 
    <div class="soup">
      <h3>General Soup</h3>
      <p> Chicken Soup $5.99</p>
      <p> Seafood Soup $7.99</p>
      <p> Beef Soup $8.99</p>
      <p> Veg Soup $4.99</p>
    </div> 
    <div class="main-area">
      <h2>Welcomes to Sushirama, gourmet sushi</h2> 
      <input placeholder="search menu">
      <button>Search</button>
    </div> 
    <div class="total">
      <p>Total: </p> 
      <p id="total-box"></p> 
      <p>Items: </p> 
      <p id="item-box"></p> 
    </div> 
    <div id="ordersheading">
      <p id="orderinfo">Orders</p>
    </div> 
    <div class="orders">
      <p class="scroll-box" id="order-history"></p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="footer">
      <h2>2025 LLC</h2> 
      <p>Located 5569 North Street, Myrtle Beach, SC, 29577</p>
      <p>912-445-6789</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="image">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"> 
    </div> 
   </div> 

    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
